{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Make a section with a light cream background, a centered editable heading and subheading, and a bold call-to-action button underneath; surround the text block with multiple customer photo cards displayed in rounded frames; on desktop, arrange the images in a balanced grid around the text with even spacing; on mobile, place the heading, subheading, and button at the top followed by a horizontal carousel of customer photos that auto-scrolls infinitely with adjustable scroll speed controls and also allows users to swipe manually to navigate through the images.
{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
